Moya Gerber and her sister Rone Odendaal were driving through the Kruger National Park in South Africa . 
  They spotted a male and female lion trying to bring down a Cape Buffalo in the park . 
  The pair stopped to photograph the struggle but the buffalo ran for the road . 
  The buffalo punctured a car wheel before running into the side of Ms Gerber's car . 
  The family were on holiday in the national park when the incident happened . 
 